# .gitattributes — Meister Repo Hygiene (Track 5)

# fixtures/ — large generated media for iOS simulator testing
# ========================================================
# Decision (2026-05, Track 5.2): Option B — KEEP in-repo.
#
# - Total: 22 MiB (largevideo_0.mp4 + RPReplay_*.mp4 dominate).
# - NOT small enough to justify LFS migration or extraction to a
#   separate test-fixtures repository (see docs/repo-hygiene.md).
# - ALL files are GENERATED by scripts/seed_photos.py (deterministic,
#   seed=42, ffmpeg + PIL). They exist for convenience so developers
#   can run:
#       python3 scripts/seed_photos.py ./fixtures
#       xcrun simctl addmedia <udid> ./fixtures/*
#   without installing heavy deps or waiting for generation every time.
#
# - Do not manually add new large media here.
# - If you need to refresh: delete the contents and re-run the generator.
# - Revisit decision only if (a) generator is deleted or (b) size grows >2x
#   without corresponding repo growth.
#
# Binary media — mark as such to avoid diff noise
fixtures/*.jpg binary
fixtures/*.png binary
fixtures/*.mp4 binary
